## 📡 All API Endpoints

| Method | Endpoint | Purpose | File |
|--------|----------|---------|------|
| `POST` | `/webhook/whatsapp` | Receives real Twilio webhook | [webhook.js](file:///E:/ANTIGRAVITY/Projects/GPT%20chatbot/server/routes/webhook.js) |
| `POST` | `/api/simulate` | Fake an incoming message (dev test) | [simulate.js](file:///E:/ANTIGRAVITY/Projects/GPT%20chatbot/server/routes/simulate.js) |
| `GET` | `/api/messages` | All messages (filterable by platform/status/search) | [messages.js](file:///E:/ANTIGRAVITY/Projects/GPT%20chatbot/server/routes/messages.js) |
| `GET` | `/api/messages/stats` | Live stat counts | [messages.js](file:///E:/ANTIGRAVITY/Projects/GPT%20chatbot/server/routes/messages.js) |
| `GET` | `/api/messages/activity` | Activity feed (last 20 events) | [messages.js](file:///E:/ANTIGRAVITY/Projects/GPT%20chatbot/server/routes/messages.js) |
| `GET` | `/api/review` | Review queue items | [review.js](file:///E:/ANTIGRAVITY/Projects/GPT%20chatbot/server/routes/review.js) |
| `POST` | `/api/review/:id/approve` | Approve draft (can edit before sending) | [review.js](file:///E:/ANTIGRAVITY/Projects/GPT%20chatbot/server/routes/review.js) |
| `POST` | `/api/review/:id/dismiss` | Dismiss without sending | [review.js](file:///E:/ANTIGRAVITY/Projects/GPT%20chatbot/server/routes/review.js) |
| `GET` | `/api/contacts` | List all VIP contacts | [contacts.js](file:///E:/ANTIGRAVITY/Projects/GPT%20chatbot/server/routes/contacts.js) |
| `POST` | `/api/contacts` | Add a new contact | [contacts.js](file:///E:/ANTIGRAVITY/Projects/GPT%20chatbot/server/routes/contacts.js) |
| `PATCH` | `/api/contacts/:id` | Update directive/autoApprove | [contacts.js](file:///E:/ANTIGRAVITY/Projects/GPT%20chatbot/server/routes/contacts.js) |
| `DELETE` | `/api/contacts/:id` | Remove a contact | [contacts.js](file:///E:/ANTIGRAVITY/Projects/GPT%20chatbot/server/routes/contacts.js) |
| `GET` | `/health` | Server health + service status | [index.js](file:///E:/ANTIGRAVITY/Projects/GPT%20chatbot/server/index.js) |

