## 🚧 What's Not Done Yet

| Feature | Status | Notes |
|---------|--------|-------|
| **Database** (MongoDB/Postgres) | ❌ Not started | Using in-memory store — data lost on restart |
| **Settings → Backend sync** | ❌ UI only | Threshold/persona/API keys in frontend don't save |
| **DND / Deep Work Mode** | ❌ UI only | Toggle exists but doesn't affect AI behavior |
| **"URGENT" Breakthrough keyword** | ❌ Not started | Spec'd but not implemented |
| **Morning Executive Summary** | ❌ Not started | Phase 4 feature |
| **Instagram / Facebook integration** | ❌ Not started | Phase 4 feature |
| **Persona training from chat history** | ❌ Not started | Vector DB (Pinecone/Weaviate) not integrated |
| **Twilio webhook signature validation** | ⚠️ Built, not wired | [validateTwilioSignature](file:///E:/ANTIGRAVITY/Projects/GPT%20chatbot/server/services/twilio.js#53-74) in twilio.js but not used as middleware |
| **Real-time updates (WebSocket)** | ❌ Not started | Currently uses polling every 4s |

