## 🚀 How to Run

```bash
# Terminal 1 — Backend
cd server
npm install
cp .env.example .env        # fill in keys (or leave as placeholder for demo)
npm run dev                  # starts on http://localhost:3001

# Terminal 2 — Frontend
cd client
npm install
npm run dev                  # starts on http://localhost:5174
```

Open `http://localhost:5174` → you'll see the dashboard. Use the **Simulate panel** to fake incoming messages and watch the AI + Review Queue in action.
